  "description": "Missing Polish Translations in Programs Section\n\nComplete Polish language translations for all content in the /pl/programs/ section of the website.\n\nRequirements:\n- Audit all pages under /pl/programs/ to identify untranslated content\n- Translate all English text that appears in the Polish version including:\n  - Page titles and headings\n  - Body content and descriptions\n  - Navigation elements and breadcrumbs\n  - Button labels and CTAs\n  - Form labels and validation messages\n  - Error messages and tooltips\n  - Meta descriptions and SEO content\n- Ensure translations are contextually appropriate and use proper Polish grammar\n- Maintain consistency with existing Polish translations elsewhere on the site\n- Verify all translated content displays correctly without layout issues\n- Test that language-specific formatting (dates, numbers, currency) is correct\n- Update translation files or CMS entries as appropriate for the project structure",
